ottky barrier at the FeNi film/Sitall (TiO2) interface. Then, in the system\nwith nanoscale circular domains, the observed anomalous paramagnetic-like\nmagnetization response can be associated with a large orbital moment of the\nlocalized electrons. The observed magnetization response is determined by the\ninterplay between the paramagnetic- and diamagnetic-like contributions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Dec 2015 12:55:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Oct 2016 12:19:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 9 Apr 2018 20:25:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-11"}
